{"tid":2510742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府上年度財政赤字2325億元","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:45:31.000Z","uid":56115,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e29722733b20da985d171c70f8eeca00bdee02e1","tid":2510742,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"政府公布2020至2021年度財務狀況的臨時數字，期內政府整體開支為8,160億元，收入為5,642億元。計及政府在綠色債券計畫下發行的<span class=\"red\">綠色債券所得淨收入193億元</span>後，政府在本財政年度錄得2,325億元赤字。<br />\n<br />\n截至3月31日為止，<span class=\"red\">本港財政儲備為9,278億元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n臨時數字相對於原來預算，政府開支方面增加849億元，增幅11.6%；收入方面減少83億元，減幅1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n本年度綜合赤字，較修訂預算的2,576億港元減少251億元。其中收入比預測增加207億港元，這主要由於<span class=\"red\">印花稅增加100億元</span>，以及入息及利得稅增加了70億元收入均較預期為高。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，政府開支較修訂預算減少了44億港元，主要由於開支需要較預期少。"},{"pid":"0b124c3773e79d80241feb4b03dbc9a5320250ab","tid":2510742,"uid":1550,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"赤字但係某啲人仲加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cb91e0bcf069e5a04bb00adc90dcb5bc5eaee4","tid":2510742,"uid":279298,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"一於加市民稅啦仲諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71053f8228c3560295f60485b283d34ae25b847","tid":2510742,"uid":279298,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"我代表全香港市民贊成加薪俸稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfe0f21980fdf389033bfce5dd2aa93af835f47","tid":2510742,"uid":21896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"增加印花稅喇，樓市咁暢旺，幾多稅都阻止唔到香港人買樓"},{"pid":"58732de2d37ce182615eb1a551541602cd976254","tid":2510742,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ef704f90b2dac9f35d692